data.description: Pleased to bring you 308 St. Louis Street lofts unit 116 in this very popular area of downtown Mobile! This is a studio condo with right at 1230 square feet. Many updates throughout, very high exposed metal rafter ceilings and stainless appliance package. St. Louis street is undergoing many new developments and renovations and close to coffee shops, restaurants, breweries, a grocery store and all of the other fun downtown things. This condo comes with garage parking with your own deeded space. If you're looking to be downtown, don't miss your opportunity to check out this space!
